targets.rawSql: select count(distinct id) from coproductionprocess;

panels.title: Total number of co-prod processes
Total Number of Interlinkers Deployed (log)
Deployed Knowledge Interlinkers

targets.rawSql:
SELECT c.coproductionprocess_id, count(distinct( b.user_id ))
FROM       team a
INNER JOIN association_user_team b ON (a.id = b.team_id)
INNER JOIN permission            c ON (a.id = c.team_id)
group by c.coproductionprocess_id
order by c.coproductionprocess_id;

panels.title: T002 Number of users per co-production process

targets.rawSql:
SELECT a.type, count(distinct(b.user_id))
FROM team a
INNER JOIN association_user_team b ON (a.id = b.team_id)
group by a.type
order by a.type;

panels.title: T003 Number of users per user type (business role) in all processes
Deployed Knowledge Interlinkers vs time

targets.rawSql:
SELECT c.coproductionprocess_id, a.type, count(distinct(b.user_id))
FROM team a
INNER JOIN association_user_team b ON (a.id = b.team_id)
INNER JOIN permission            c ON (a.id = c.team_id)
group by c.coproductionprocess_id, a.type
order by c.coproductionprocess_id, a.type;

targets.rawSql:
select coproductionprocess_id, count(distinct id)
from asset
group by coproductionprocess_id
order by count desc;

panels.title: T024a Num. used INTERLINKERs (all types) per co-prod. process

targets.rawSql:
select b.coproductionprocess_id, count(distinct a.id)
from internalasset a
inner join asset b on (a.id = b.id)
where a.knowledgeinterlinker_id is not null
group by b.coproductionprocess_id
order by count desc;

panels.title: T024b Num. used Knowledge INTERLINKERs per co-prod. process

targets.rawSql:
select b.coproductionprocess_id, count(distinct a.id)
from internalasset a
inner join asset b on (a.id = b.id)
where a.softwareinterlinker_id is not null and a.knowledgeinterlinker_id is null
group by b.coproductionprocess_id
order by count desc;

panels.title: T024c Num. used internal SW INTERLINKERs per co-prod. process

targets.rawSql:
select coproductionprocess_id, count(distinct id)
from asset
where type = 'externalasset'
group by coproductionprocess_id;

panels.title: T024d Num. used external SW INTERLINKERs per co-prod. process

targets.rawSql:
select a.schema_used, count(distinct b.id)
from coproductionprocess a
inner join asset b on (a.id=b.coproductionprocess_id)
group by a.schema_used
order by count desc;

panels.title: T025 Num. used INTERLINKERs per schema TYPE

targets.rawSql:
select b.coproductionprocess_id, a.schema_used, count(distinct b.id)
from coproductionprocess a
inner join asset b on (a.id=b.coproductionprocess_id)
group by b.coproductionprocess_id, a.schema_used
order by count desc;

panels.title: T026 Num. used INTERLINKERs per co-prod. process per schema type

targets.rawSql:
select b.phase_id, a.schema_used, count(distinct b.id)
from coproductionprocess a
inner join asset b on (a.id=b.coproductionprocess_id)
inner join phase c on (c.id=b.phase_id)
group by b.phase_id, a.schema_used
order by count desc;

panels.title: T027 INTERLINKER IDs used per co-prod. phase per schema type
